  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "これは「メダロット」シリーズの第3作目です。このタイトルでは、戦闘中に特定のメダロットを変形させてその能力を変更することができます。個別の戦闘に加えて、プレイヤーは3人対戦も楽しむことができます。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Medarot 3 was released in 2000 for the Game Boy Color. It was released in two versions: Kabuto and Kuwagata.\n\nThe game follows Ikki Tenryou and his friends in the town of Omikuji. After Ikki robottles with the Screws, everyone's Medarotch data is suddenly deleted by an unknown figure.\n\nMedarot 3 introduced various new gameplay aspects, including Medachange and Medalias.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ],
